text: Choi Myeong-jong (born 6 May 1933) is a South Korean wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle welterweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of South Korea Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sport wrestlers from Seoul Category:Wrestlers at the 1958 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for South Korea
